ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectMemorandum of Understanding between Canada and the United Nations Contributing Resources to the United Nations Multidimensional Integrated Stabilization Mission in Mali
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate the authority to sign, on behalf of Canada, and to bring into force for Canada, the MEMORANDUM OF UNDERSTANDING BETWEEN CANADA AND THE UNITED NATIONS CONTRIBUTING RESOURCES TO THE UNITED NATIONS MULTIDIMENSIONAL INTEGRATE STABILIZATION MISSION IN MALI.
